    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Check out <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/Arrays.html#copyOfRange%28boolean[],%20int,%20int%29\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">copyOfRange</a>; and example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>int[] arr2 = Arrays.copyOfRange(arr,0,3);\n</code></pre>\n"
