    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You could wrap your array as a list, and request a sublist of it.</p>\n\n<pre><code>MyClass[] array = ...;\nList&lt;MyClass&gt; subArray = Arrays.asList(array).subList(index, array.length);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 35717,
      "reputation" : 134823,
      "user_id" : 101258,
